text: Coen de Koning (born 5 April 1983) is a Dutch competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the mixed Nacra 17. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of the Netherlands Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Nacra 17 Category:People from Hoorn
